{
  "stem": "13623.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We don't know where, but we're being told to walk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "When the-- the soldiers, the guards that were watching us, realized that were too many women and children that are not going to be able to make it, they're not going to be able to walk, they ordered the local gentile population that had horse and buggies to bring all the horse and buggies to us.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they loaded all the old people, the women, and the children, and the horse and buggies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they followed us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The man were up front.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The women were following behind us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was a warm May day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we were walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was a snake of people as far as the eye can see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were walking, but we don't know where.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "As we pass little villages on the way to wherever they're taking us, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the local gentile population were standing on the street.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they were watching us like-- like you watch, these days, a circus go by.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As the day wore on and we were walking, our baggage got heavier and heavier.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The-- the heat got to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We perspired.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And people started to drop their baggage just on the side of the road.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "The local population, at first, were kind of shy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They were-- they didn't know how to act.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Our guards encouraged them, go pick it up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "It's yours.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Go take it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were like-- they were watching and followed us and picking up stuff, whatever, when we got tired enough to carrying that valise, that package, whatever we carried.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "When we threw it down, they picked it up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And no questions asked, it was theirs.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
